item.description:
Free concert in Goodwill Park on Tuesday, July 12.

The band is Gumbo Diablo described as: "an eclectic group of veteran musicians who serve up a killer mix of zydeco, New Orleans r&b, Latin, reggae, and roots rock. They're best compared to the rock bands Los Lobos, Jimmy Cliff and Buckweat Zydeco."

Goodwill park is on Green St., right in the center of town. If you're coming from Rte 495, it's on your left and right before Holliston Superette. If you're coming from the east, it's right after Holliston Superette. (BTW, they have great sandwiches, etc.)

I'll be in the back in the middle with a brown and pink chair.
item.name: FREE SUMMER CONCERT IN HOLLISTON
